(or 軍荼)kuṇḍa, a hole in the ground for the fire at the fire altar: thehomaor fire altar.

吠
To bark (as a dog); translit.ve,vi,vai; cf. 毘; 鞞; 衛; 別.

吠世師
吠世史迦 Vaiśeṣika, v. 衛.

吠努璃耶
vaiḍūrya, lapis lazuli.

吠嚧遮那
吠路者那, Vairocana v. 毘.

吠室囉末拏
Vaiśravaṇa, v. 鞞.

