Bhādrapadā, the 壁 constellation in Pegasus and Andromeda. Bhadrā, a female disciple of Śākyamuni. Guṇabhadra, v. 求, anāga-king; a tree.

跋陀羅樓支
Bhadraruci, v. 跋羅縷支.

