應理宗
(應理圓實宗) A name of the Dharmalakṣana school, 法相宗 q.v.

應用無邊
Omnipresent response to need; universal ability to aid.

應病與藥
To give medicine suited to the disease, the Buddha's mode of teaching.

應真
