禪悅
Joy of the mystic trance. 禪悅食 Its mystic nourishing powers.

禪慧
The mystic trance and wisdom.

禪房
Meditation abode, a room for meditation, a cell, a hermitage, general name for a monastery.

禪教
The teaching of the Chan sect. Also, 禪 the esoteric tradition and 教 the teaching of the scriptures.

禪智
Meditation and wisdom, of. 禪卷.

